        "body_1": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>At Soundbrenner we firmly believe success is not given, it's earned. This is true for musicians, but also for companies.</p><p>We went to great lengths to ensure the product you’re holding was made to the highest standards. We care deeply that it becomes an irreplaceable companion on your musical journey.</p><p>If you experience any issues, our team will work hard to put a smile back on your face. We’re just an e-mail away.</p>"
          }
