        },
        "heading_iGiUqd": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Where to wear it"
          }
        },
        "image_FAEFwi": {
          "type": "image",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Product_Pulse_Order_9.jpg"
          }
        },
        "text_TGD86k": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Where you wear the Pulse on your body can have a big impact on your experience, and the best position can vary for each musician.</p><p>The included short and long bands allow you to wear the Pulse on your wrist, arm, or ankle. During your first few sessions, try different positions to find what works best for you.</p><p>Make sure to keep the band snug. A tighter fit will make the vibrations feel stronger.</p><p>The hooks on the long band allow you to easily slide it over your arm.</p>"
          }
        },
        "image_qgC4HK": {
          "type": "image",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Product_Pulse_Order_10.png"
          }
        },
        "text_GK4Gkx": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Did you know we also offer a body strap for the chest, shoulder, or thigh? It allows you to feel the beat even more clearly. You can find it here:</p>"
